===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ar|en}} {{term|القُرْآن|tr=al-qurʾān|lang=ar}}, definite form of {{term|قُرْآن||tr=qurʾān|act of reciting|lang=ar}}, verbal noun of {{term|قَرَأَ||tr=qaraʾa|to recite; to read (aloud)|lang=ar}}. Compare {{etyl|syc|-}} {{term|ܩܪܝܢܐ||tr=qeryānā|reading; scripture|lang=syc|sc=Syrc}}.

